tid":242122,"uid":75435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n好熱會叫溫度高<br />\n凍叫溫度低<br />\n咁無溫度=唔凍唔熱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申商科撚"},{"pid":"b75e607bd91797659d1068b6553ed0acc333159d","tid":242122,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:55:43.000Z","msg":"知道温度點產生<br />\n<br />\n咪知道點樣唔令空度產生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇讀phy"},{"pid":"c3faa690d20846488ac80a23ee6717a147ba1216","tid":242122,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學嘢<br />\n好熱會叫溫度高<br />\n凍叫溫度低<br />\n咁無溫度=唔凍唔熱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申商科撚</blockquote><br />\n熱同凍係對應返我地人體嘅温度<br />\n<br />\n高過我地體温就熱<br />\n低過就凍<br />\n人體有enzyme, 好似高度40度就會denature, 唔識好記得<br />\n<br />\n中學bio 嘢"},{"pid":"96f430ea08eba66704d8847fe1e8415fe253a85a","tid":242122,"uid":105863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"無溫度我諗係叫絕對0度，0K=零下273.15攝氏度<br />\n就算外太空都有溫度，大約4K到，好似係<br />\n因為大爆炸之後有殘餘能量<br />\n<br />\n利申：幾年前中學程度physics, 等俾大學撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd24cc0abc07a22c59c46a4476a1d28d9a4abc6","tid":242122,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"溫度係interval 唔係ratio<br />\nInterval 姐係可以分高低但唔一定跟比例<br />\n正如二十度唔係十度既兩倍咁熱<br />\nRatio 就好似錢咁 二十蚊就係十蚊既兩倍 而零蚊就係冇錢咁解<br />\n<br />\n所以就算0度都唔代表冇溫度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26fac0a796a4cf7fbca4b5dc44e0b6c5dabeedc